@Node Drefresh "Command Reference : drefresh"
   DRefresh


This command refreshes the debug display. 'drefresh' is only useful when
you are in fullscreen debugging mode.

See the @{" prefs " Link "Prefs"}, @{" dwin " Link "Dwin"} and @{" swin " Link "Swin"} commands to install the fullscreen
debugger.


